data.title: Eastern Harbor Media, LLC
data.meta_description: Eastern Harbor Media, LLC | 156 followers on LinkedIn. Eastern Harbor Media is a rapidly growing digital news publisher.   Eastern Harbor's flagship publication is The National Memo (NationalMemo.com), a progressive website and e-newsletter which reaches 800,000-plus dedicated readers each morning. Building digital media to drive social change, Eastern Harbor develops relationships with its audience and works with high-profile advertisers to reach decision makers, activists, and avid consumers.
